    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0157回】 抱持著目標與目的</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0101-0200/t-0157-aim-your-way/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 23:50:47 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0101-0200/t-0157-aim-your-way/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
  /* 1. 標題縮小 */
