    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0318回】 技的磨練要靠自己</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0301-0400/t-0318-skill-self-refine/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Feb 2026 22:46:41 +0800</pubDate>
